= Radiant Blog Extension

Adds add access control functionality to Radiant. Currently maintained by http://github.com/istar

== Patches

If you want to contribute features or fixes please write your specs and code and submit pull requests to these github.com users:

- istar

== Installation

To install Comments, run:

  rake radiant:extensions:comments:migrate


== More Help

This rdiant-blog-extension add bloger role to Radiant
If your website have blog function, and the blog writed by different people, this extension can help you well.



